flowRoot.flowPara: Figure S8. The list of all genes that are essential in at least one of the genomes in this study that are also annotated in KEGG pathways. Red shows essential genes and green shows non-essential genes. Black shows that the gene does not exist in that genome and 'D' means that the gene has paralogs in that genome. The numbers next to some gene names indicate that the gene is involved in multiple pathways.
